-F, --list-formats
	List all available formats

-x, --extract-audio
	Convert video files to audio-only files (requires ffmpeg or avconv and ffprobe or avprobe)

--audio-format FORMAT
	Specify audio format: "best", "aac", "vorbis", "mp3", "m4a", "opus", or "wav"; "best" by default

--audio-quality QUALITY
	Specify ffmpeg/avconv audio quality, insert a value between 0 (better) and 9 (worse) for VBR or a spe‚Äê
cific bitrate like 128K (default 5)

# download best mp3 of video
	youtube-dl -x --audio-format mp3 --audio-quality 0 '<url>'
